author: AP
title: Minor leaguers, college players try to stay ready for baseball's return
description: Baseball players are trying any way they can to stay ready amid the uncertainty of whether there will even be a season this year.
content:
ALAMEDA, Calif. Andre Nnebe hollers over the breeze coming off the bay behind home plate and announces to the group, First pitch, 2:10!
